  "description": "Diagnosing broken SAML SSO into Salesforce \u2014 IdP-initiated vs SP-initiated flows, signing-certificate validity / expiry, NameID format mismatches, RelayState handling, audience / entityId / issuer mismatches, clock skew, the SAML Assertion Validator in Setup, the Login History debug log, and the My Domain prerequisite for SSO. Covers the standard diagnostic loop: read the SAML response, identify which check failed, fix at the IdP or SP. NOT for OAuth / OpenID Connect SSO (see security/oauth-openid-troubleshooting), NOT for setting up SSO from scratch (see security/sso-saml-setup).",
